summary: WILLIAM P. MURPHY, JR. was a physician at Harvard Medical School and the National Institutes of Health. He also worked at St. Francis Hospital, Honolulu, Hawaii, and Fenval Laboratories, Inc., Framingham, Massachusetts. His work was published in the prestigious journal, "The Journal of Medical Research"
